```bash
# Get overall cluster status
â†’ "Show me the OpenStack cluster status"
â†’ Calls: get_openstack_cluster_status()

# Check service health
â†’ "Are all OpenStack services running properly?"
â†’ Calls: get_openstack_service_status()

# Monitor resource usage
â†’ "What's the current resource utilization?"
â†’ Calls: monitor_openstack_resources()

# Get instance details
â†’ "Show details for instance web-server-01"
â†’ Calls: get_openstack_instance_details("web-server-01")
```

### ðŸŒ Network Examples

```bash
# Check all networks
â†’ "Show me all network configurations"
â†’ Calls: get_openstack_network_details("all")

# Specific network details
â†’ "Get details for the internal network"
â†’ Calls: get_openstack_network_details("internal")
```

### âš™ï¸ Management Examples

```bash
